Detailed Description

EDI-Version : 4.25A This header file contains public declarations for the high level library.

This header file contains public declarations for the high level library.


This library allows access to ETEL hardware like drives, UltimET, etc...
Once connected, it is possible to get and set registers, executing command and different functions on the hardware itself.
This library is conformed to POSIX 1003.1c
